Package com.intellij.codeInspection.dataFlow

Interface TypeConstraint.Exact

  • All Superinterfaces:
    TypeConstraint
    Enclosing interface:
    TypeConstraint

    public static interface TypeConstraint.Exact
extends TypeConstraint
    Represents an exact type. It may also represent types that cannot be instantiated (e.g. interface types), so no object could satisfy them, but they are still useful as building blocks for TypeConstraint.Constrained.
